        "cooked": "<p>I am going over the git for RBAC and trying to understand how to use this? How can I grant a user read only access and read write and accordingly?</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/FoundationDB/fdb-kubernetes-operator/tree/90224ee73ae793f6381fee33b1bbe0e88b0ce92d/config/rbac\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://github.com/FoundationDB/fdb-kubernetes-operator/tree/90224ee73ae793f6381fee33b1bbe0e88b0ce92d/config/rbac</a></p>",
